  <prompt>
    <goal>
      Create ActionEntity and ActionTypeReference DTO classes for deserializing Dataverse Web API responses.
    </goal>
    <context>
      Actions are stored in sprk_systemprompts entity with a lookup to sprk_analysisactiontype.

      Entity schema:
      - sprk_systempromptid (Guid)
      - sprk_name (String)
      - sprk_description (Memo)
      - sprk_systemprompt (Memo) - The system prompt text
      - sprk_ActionTypeId (Lookup) → sprk_analysisactiontype

      SortOrder is extracted from type name prefix: "01 - Extraction" → 1
    </context>
    <constraints>
      - Follow existing DTO patterns
      - Use System.Text.Json attributes
    </constraints>
  </prompt>

